{"about_the_game":"<i>&quot;The City Of Machine Guns,<br>back in those days,<br>me and Richard were working for a local racketeer everybody called Pepas.<br><br>I thought things were going fine in the city,<br>but after this job,<br>I started to have my doubts about it's state.&quot;</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/extras/steam_about.png?t=1589875513\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/extras/gif_expozice.gif?t=1589875513\" /><br>The prototype is not a demo or a fully fledged game,<br>it contains only a basic structure on top of which we wish<br>to build <strong>Velvetist: The City Of Machineguns</strong>.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/extras/steam_story.png?t=1589875513\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/extras/gif_story.gif?t=1589875513\" /><br>The story of this prototype is set in the first third of the overall story.<br>You will play around with a small amount of vehicles, characters and one mission.<br>Velvetist Prototype introduce the vision of a third person action open world adventure game set in an old, socialist occupied town of the second half of the 20th century.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/extras/steam_gameplay.png?t=1589875513\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/extras/gif_gameplay.gif?t=1589875513\" /><br>Prototype introduces gameplay features such as:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>city driving and shootouts, which are tied together with cinematics that tell the story<br></li><li>simple puzzles<br></li><li>searching for lenses<br></li><li>chasing<br></li><li>carrying boxes<br></li><li>conversations and meeting new people</li></ul><br><i>Missions are made up of these basic elements, but each has its own color and the player will never be bored</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/extras/steam_support.png?t=1589875513\" /><br>If you\u00b4ll end up liking our project, please support us by adding <strong>Velvetist: The City of Machineguns</strong> in your Steam wishlist<br>It will help us greatly !<br><br>We also invite you to take part in the fun over on our <strong>Discord server</strong><br><br>where you can share funny screenshots, suggestions for improvements or any bugs you might come across<br><strong>We wish you a lot of fun playing !</strong> \u2764","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1589875513","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1589875513","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1589875513","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1589875513","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<i>&quot;The City Of Machine Guns,<br>back in those days,<br>me and Richard were working for a local racketeer everybody called Pepas.<br><br>I thought things were going fine in the city,<br>but after this job,<br>I started to have my doubts about it's state.&quot;</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/extras/steam_about.png?t=1589875513\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/extras/gif_expozice.gif?t=1589875513\" /><br>The prototype is not a demo or a fully fledged game,<br>it contains only a basic structure on top of which we wish<br>to build <strong>Velvetist: The City Of Machineguns</strong>.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/extras/steam_story.png?t=1589875513\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/extras/gif_story.gif?t=1589875513\" /><br>The story of this prototype is set in the first third of the overall story.<br>You will play around with a small amount of vehicles, characters and one mission.<br>Velvetist Prototype introduce the vision of a third person action open world adventure game set in an old, socialist occupied town of the second half of the 20th century.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/extras/steam_gameplay.png?t=1589875513\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/extras/gif_gameplay.gif?t=1589875513\" /><br>Prototype introduces gameplay features such as:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>city driving and shootouts, which are tied together with cinematics that tell the story<br></li><li>simple puzzles<br></li><li>searching for lenses<br></li><li>chasing<br></li><li>carrying boxes<br></li><li>conversations and meeting new people</li></ul><br><i>Missions are made up of these basic elements, but each has its own color and the player will never be bored</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/extras/steam_support.png?t=1589875513\" /><br>If you\u00b4ll end up liking our project, please support us by adding <strong>Velvetist: The City of Machineguns</strong> in your Steam wishlist<br>It will help us greatly !<br><br>We also invite you to take part in the fun over on our <strong>Discord server</strong><br><br>where you can share funny screenshots, suggestions for improvements or any bugs you might come across<br><strong>We wish you a lot of fun playing !</strong> \u2764","developers":["SiCzech Arts"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173330/header.jpg?t=1589875513","is_free":true,"legal_notice":"The Naked Game uses the Unreal\u00ae Engine.<br />\r\nUnreal\u00ae is a trademark or registered trademark of Epic Games, Inc. in the United States of America and elsewhere<br />\r\nUnreal\u00ae Engine,<br />\r\nCopyright 1998 \u2013 2015, Epic Games, Inc. All rights reserved. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nCopyright \u00a9 The Naked Game, Czech Republic. All rights reserved.","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256785835,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256785835/movie480.mp4?t=1589833612","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256785835/movie_max.mp4?t=1589833612"},"name":"VELVETIST: Prototype | Launch Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256785835/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1589833612","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256785835/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1589833612","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256785835/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1589833612"}},{"highlight":true,"id":256782776,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256782776/movie480.mp4?t=1588336705","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256782776/movie_max.mp4?t=1588336705"},"name":"VELVETIST: Prototype Exposition Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256782776/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1588336705","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/